this is my room.

19
00:01:24,680 --> 00:01:25,240
I'll go out, then.

20
00:01:28,320 --> 00:01:29,680
You keep wearing this necklace.

21
00:01:30,080 --> 00:01:31,560
Is it special to you?

22
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:33,760
What has it got to do with you?

23
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:38,080
Did you

24
